WEBVTT

00:01.415 --> 00:03.138
JOST: <i>Albert Einstein.</i>

00:03.139 --> 00:04.838
Your reputation precedes you.

00:04.839 --> 00:06.842
HERMANN: <i>Your mother,
sister and I are moving</i>

00:06.843 --> 00:09.211
- to Italy.
- So you're abandoning me?

00:09.212 --> 00:11.946
HERMANN: <i>No! I'm looking
out for your future.</i>

00:11.947 --> 00:12.891
PAULINE: <i>How is Marie?</i>

00:12.892 --> 00:14.702
EINSTEIN: <i>Wonderful.
She's teaching me French.</i>

00:14.703 --> 00:16.805
HERMANN: <i>You will go back to
Munich, and that is an order.</i>

00:16.806 --> 00:17.651
I'm sorry, Father,

00:17.652 --> 00:19.086
but I'm not going back to Germany.

00:19.087 --> 00:21.801
- It is time to stand up for Germany!
- (applause)

00:21.802 --> 00:23.748
Tell me, my son, uh, the genius,

00:23.749 --> 00:26.207
how do you propose to make
a living without a job?

00:26.208 --> 00:27.292
I'm going to be a professor.

00:27.293 --> 00:29.302
HERMANN: <i>You failed your entrance exam!</i>

00:29.303 --> 00:30.355
EINSTEIN: <i>I won't fail again.</i>

00:30.356 --> 00:31.601
Welcome to Zurich Polytechnic.

00:31.602 --> 00:33.485
EINSTEIN: I apologize,
I didn't think...

00:33.486 --> 00:35.049
That a woman could possibly understand

00:35.050 --> 00:37.382
the Maxwell-Faraday equation.

00:37.383 --> 00:39.811
Einstein, say hello to Mileva Maric.

